question: The population of 50,000 to 99,999 falls under which of the following class as specified by the census department?
explanation: Classes and population specified by the census department are Class I- 100,000 and more. Class II- 50,000 to 99,999. Class III- 20,000 to 49,999. Class IV- 10,000 to 19,999. Class V- 5000 to 9999. Class VI- Less 5000.
